snippet.title: Plants (gameplay)
snippet.description:
Gameplay of the game Plants.
In Plants you control a flower and let it grow while enjoying the scenery. There is only one goal: enjoy your experience.

Play Plants here: www.rogerty.com

Twitter: @RogertyGames
